SIMPLE: curiousness
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Curiousness
<hw>Cu"ri*ous*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Carefulness;
painstaking.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My father's care⟦br⟧
With <qex>curiousness</qex> and cost did train me up.</q> <rj><qau>
Massinger.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being curious; exactness of
workmanship; ingenuity of contrivance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Inquisitiveness; curiosity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>curium</ent>⟦br⟧
